main event: A civilian observer reported seeing a large, round object with three white lights in front pass overhead in North Sacramento, California.
interesting points: The object made a loud, clear humming sound that was not like a jet aircraft.
The object was approximately 50 feet wide and passed over the observer at an angle of 45 degrees from the ground, about 100 feet in height.
The duration of the sighting was 30 seconds.
A C-124 aircraft landed at a nearby air force base approximately 22 minutes after the sighting.
The preparing officer felt the observer was a highly excitable person who may have mistaken the C-124 aircraft for the UFO.
sighted object: large, round object with three white lights in front
witnesses: one civilian observer, a 25-year-old divorced housewife
